				"This is a mini-boss (??), where it seemingly responds differently when shot at different times. (Maybe RNG, but not very apparent). When I notice the difference in responses, I then realized a "one" round kill was possible, whereas MrTASer has to back up slightly to continue shooting again.
			]td
