			]td
			[td 
				"This was an interesting discovery. It appears that when the mini-boss gets hit, collision detection is avoided on the helicopter. I'm 50% sure about this, but nevertheless...I was able to shoot earlier by moving downwards more, shooting later, and starting my forward movement 3 frames faster.
			]td
